{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":618,"text":"When I was born,"},{"time":2056,"text":"there was really only one book"},{"time":3736,"text":"about how to raise your children,"},{"time":5622,"text":"and it was written by Dr. Spock."},{"time":8789,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":10725,"text":"Thank you for indulging me."},{"time":11956,"text":"I have always wanted to do that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":15562,"text":"No, it was Benjamin Spock,"},{"time":17665,"text":"and his book was called \"The Common\nSense Book of Baby And Child Care.\""},{"time":21515,"text":"It sold almost 50 million copies \nby the time he died."},{"time":27162,"text":"Today, I, as the mother of a six-year-old,"},{"time":30807,"text":"walk into Barnes and Noble,"},{"time":32484,"text":"and see this."},{"time":35165,"text":"And it is amazing"},{"time":37124,"text":"the variety that one finds \non those shelves."},{"time":40828,"text":"There are guides to raising \nan eco-friendly kid,"},{"time":45250,"text":"a gluten-free kid,"},{"time":47445,"text":"a disease-proof kid,"},{"time":49810,"text":"which, if you ask me, is a little bit creepy."},{"time":53763,"text":"There are guides to raising a bilingual kid"},{"time":56300,"text":"even if you only speak one language at home."},{"time":59151,"text":"There are guides to raising a financially savvy kid"},{"time":62767,"text":"and a science-minded kid"},{"time":65529,"text":"and a kid who is a whiz at yoga."},{"time":68639,"text":"Short of teaching your toddler how to defuse"},{"time":71849,"text":"a nuclear bomb,"},{"time":73199,"text":"there is pretty much a guide to everything."}]},{"cues":[{"time":79705,"text":"All of these books are well-intentioned."},{"time":82319,"text":"I am sure that many of them are great."},{"time":86829,"text":"But taken together, I am sorry,"},{"time":90930,"text":"I do not see help"},{"time":93281,"text":"when I look at that shelf."},{"time":97130,"text":"I see anxiety."},{"time":99404,"text":"I see a giant candy-colored monument"},{"time":102131,"text":"to our collective panic,"},{"time":105074,"text":"and it makes me want to know,"},{"time":107655,"text":"why is it that raising our children"},{"time":110038,"text":"is associated with so much anguish"},{"time":111820,"text":"and so much confusion?"},{"time":114078,"text":"Why is it that we are at sixes and sevens"},{"time":116792,"text":"about the one thing human beings"},{"time":119768,"text":"have been doing successfully for millennia,"},{"time":121632,"text":"long before parenting message boards"},{"time":124468,"text":"and peer-reviewed studies came along?"},{"time":127345,"text":"Why is it that so many mothers and fathers"},{"time":129998,"text":"experience parenthood as a kind of crisis?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":136220,"text":"Crisis might seem like a strong word,"},{"time":138566,"text":"but there is data suggesting it probably isn't."},{"time":141544,"text":"There was, in fact, a paper of just this very name,"},{"time":144300,"text":"\"Parenthood as Crisis,\" published in 1957,"},{"time":148386,"text":"and in the 50-plus years since,"},{"time":150924,"text":"there has been plenty of scholarship"},{"time":153010,"text":"documenting a pretty clear pattern"},{"time":155417,"text":"of parental anguish."},{"time":157472,"text":"Parents experience more stress than non-parents."},{"time":160778,"text":"Their marital satisfaction is lower."},{"time":163694,"text":"There have been a number of studies"},{"time":165211,"text":"looking at how parents feel"},{"time":166500,"text":"when they are spending time with their kids,"},{"time":168917,"text":"and the answer often is, not so great."},{"time":172817,"text":"Last year, I spoke with a researcher"},{"time":174855,"text":"named Matthew Killingsworth"},{"time":176151,"text":"who is doing a very, very imaginative project"},{"time":179611,"text":"that tracks people's happiness,"},{"time":181509,"text":"and here is what he told me he found:"},{"time":185478,"text":"\"Interacting with your friends"},{"time":187092,"text":"is better than interacting with your spouse,"},{"time":190004,"text":"which is better than interacting with other relatives,"},{"time":193360,"text":"which is better than interacting with acquaintances,"},{"time":196585,"text":"which is better than interacting with parents,"},{"time":199530,"text":"which is better than interacting with children."},{"time":203306,"text":"Who are on par with strangers.\""},{"time":205306,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":209812,"text":"But here's the thing."},{"time":212179,"text":"I have been looking at what underlies these data"},{"time":215257,"text":"for three years,"},{"time":217168,"text":"and children are not the problem."},{"time":220394,"text":"Something about parenting right now at this moment"},{"time":225381,"text":"is the problem."},{"time":227421,"text":"Specifically, I don't think we know"},{"time":229910,"text":"what parenting is supposed to be."},{"time":232426,"text":"Parent, as a verb,"},{"time":234606,"text":"only entered common usage in 1970."},{"time":238868,"text":"Our roles as mothers and fathers have changed."},{"time":242190,"text":"The roles of our children have changed."},{"time":245031,"text":"We are all now furiously improvising"},{"time":247373,"text":"our way through a situation"},{"time":249279,"text":"for which there is no script,"},{"time":252872,"text":"and if you're an amazing jazz musician,"},{"time":254913,"text":"then improv is great,"},{"time":257100,"text":"but for the rest of us,"},{"time":259505,"text":"it can kind of feel like a crisis."}]},{"cues":[{"time":263321,"text":"So how did we get here?"},{"time":265901,"text":"How is it that we are all now navigating"},{"time":268017,"text":"a child-rearing universe"},{"time":269569,"text":"without any norms to guide us?"},{"time":272397,"text":"Well, for starters, there has been"},{"time":274557,"text":"a major historical change."},{"time":276396,"text":"Until fairly recently,"},{"time":278589,"text":"kids worked, on our farms primarily,"},{"time":282301,"text":"but also in factories, mills, mines."},{"time":285169,"text":"Kids were considered economic assets."},{"time":288085,"text":"Sometime during the Progressive Era,"},{"time":290181,"text":"we put an end to this arrangement."},{"time":291809,"text":"We recognized kids had rights,"},{"time":294080,"text":"we banned child labor,"},{"time":295600,"text":"we focused on education instead,"},{"time":298370,"text":"and school became a child's new work."},{"time":301546,"text":"And thank God it did."},{"time":303252,"text":"But that only made a parent's role"},{"time":305649,"text":"more confusing in a way."},{"time":307420,"text":"The old arrangement might not have been"},{"time":308972,"text":"particularly ethical, but it was reciprocal."},{"time":312090,"text":"We provided food, clothing, shelter,"},{"time":314446,"text":"and moral instruction to our kids,"},{"time":316570,"text":"and they in return provided income."}]},{"cues":[{"time":322210,"text":"Once kids stopped working,"},{"time":324178,"text":"the economics of parenting changed."},{"time":327482,"text":"Kids became, in the words of one"},{"time":330054,"text":"brilliant if totally ruthless sociologist,"},{"time":333496,"text":"\"economically worthless but emotionally priceless.\""},{"time":338258,"text":"Rather than them working for us,"},{"time":340649,"text":"we began to work for them,"},{"time":342552,"text":"because within only a matter of decades"},{"time":344412,"text":"it became clear:"},{"time":345820,"text":"if we wanted our kids to succeed,"},{"time":348190,"text":"school was not enough."},{"time":351183,"text":"Today, extracurricular activities are a kid's new work,"},{"time":355980,"text":"but that's work for us too,"},{"time":357737,"text":"because we are the ones\ndriving them to soccer practice."},{"time":360920,"text":"Massive piles of homework are a kid's new work,"},{"time":363783,"text":"but that's also work for us,"},{"time":365351,"text":"because we have to check it."},{"time":367462,"text":"About three years ago, a Texas woman"},{"time":369787,"text":"told something to me"},{"time":370841,"text":"that totally broke my heart."},{"time":374120,"text":"She said, almost casually,"},{"time":378160,"text":"\"Homework is the new dinner.\""},{"time":382594,"text":"The middle class now pours all of its time"},{"time":385194,"text":"and energy and resources into its kids,"},{"time":388636,"text":"even though the middle class"},{"time":389989,"text":"has less and less of those things to give."},{"time":393602,"text":"Mothers now spend more time with their children"},{"time":396886,"text":"than they did in 1965,"},{"time":399269,"text":"when most women were not even in the workforce."}]},{"cues":[{"time":404663,"text":"It would probably be easier for parents"},{"time":406775,"text":"to do their new roles"},{"time":408166,"text":"if they knew what they were preparing their kids for."},{"time":411731,"text":"This is yet another thing that\nmakes modern parenting"},{"time":414175,"text":"so very confounding."},{"time":416245,"text":"We have no clue what portion our wisdom, if any,"},{"time":419933,"text":"is of use to our kids."},{"time":421690,"text":"The world is changing so rapidly,"},{"time":423123,"text":"it's impossible to say."},{"time":425326,"text":"This was true even when I was young."},{"time":427401,"text":"When I was a kid, high school specifically,"},{"time":430425,"text":"I was told that I would be at sea"},{"time":432409,"text":"in the new global economy"},{"time":434194,"text":"if I did not know Japanese."},{"time":438700,"text":"And with all due respect to the Japanese,"},{"time":441202,"text":"it didn't turn out that way."},{"time":443643,"text":"Now there is a certain kind of middle-class parent"},{"time":445931,"text":"that is obsessed with teaching their kids Mandarin,"},{"time":448635,"text":"and maybe they're onto something,"},{"time":451245,"text":"but we cannot know for sure."},{"time":453980,"text":"So, absent being able to anticipate the future,"},{"time":456609,"text":"what we all do, as good parents,"},{"time":459234,"text":"is try and prepare our kids"},{"time":461161,"text":"for every possible kind of future,"},{"time":464209,"text":"hoping that just one of our efforts will pay off."},{"time":468266,"text":"We teach our kids chess,"},{"time":470194,"text":"thinking maybe they will need analytical skills."},{"time":472829,"text":"We sign them up for team sports,"},{"time":475274,"text":"thinking maybe they will need collaborative skills,"},{"time":478561,"text":"you know, for when they go\nto Harvard Business School."},{"time":481081,"text":"We try and teach them to be financially savvy"},{"time":484310,"text":"and science-minded and eco-friendly"},{"time":487767,"text":"and gluten-free,"},{"time":490733,"text":"though now is probably a good time to tell you"},{"time":492705,"text":"that I was not eco-friendly and gluten-free as a child."},{"time":498245,"text":"I ate jars of pureed macaroni and beef."},{"time":503035,"text":"And you know what? I'm doing okay."},{"time":505212,"text":"I pay my taxes."},{"time":507625,"text":"I hold down a steady job."},{"time":510842,"text":"I was even invited to speak at TED."},{"time":515170,"text":"But the presumption now is that"},{"time":516552,"text":"what was good enough for me,\nor for my folks for that matter,"},{"time":519950,"text":"isn't good enough anymore."},{"time":521761,"text":"So we all make a mad dash to that bookshelf,"},{"time":525425,"text":"because we feel like if we aren't trying everything,"},{"time":528737,"text":"it's as if we're doing nothing"},{"time":530867,"text":"and we're defaulting on our obligations to our kids."}]},{"cues":[{"time":536204,"text":"So it's hard enough to navigate our new roles"},{"time":538812,"text":"as mothers and fathers."},{"time":540334,"text":"Now add to this problem something else:"},{"time":542780,"text":"we are also navigating new roles"},{"time":544708,"text":"as husbands and wives"},{"time":546312,"text":"because most women today are in the workforce."},{"time":549960,"text":"This is another reason, I think,"},{"time":551490,"text":"that parenthood feels like a crisis."},{"time":553812,"text":"We have no rules, no scripts, no norms"},{"time":556462,"text":"for what to do when a child comes along"},{"time":559002,"text":"now that both mom and dad are breadwinners."},{"time":562193,"text":"The writer Michael Lewis once put this"},{"time":564598,"text":"very, very well."},{"time":565835,"text":"He said that the surest way"},{"time":568347,"text":"for a couple to start fighting"},{"time":570142,"text":"is for them to go out to dinner with another couple"},{"time":573170,"text":"whose division of labor"},{"time":574355,"text":"is ever so slightly different from theirs,"},{"time":577965,"text":"because the conversation in\nthe car on the way home"},{"time":581641,"text":"goes something like this:"},{"time":584775,"text":"\"So, did you catch that Dave is the one"},{"time":589408,"text":"who walks them to school every morning?\""},{"time":593309,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":597742,"text":"Without scripts telling us who does what"},{"time":600257,"text":"in this brave new world, couples fight,"},{"time":603306,"text":"and both mothers and fathers each have"},{"time":606545,"text":"their legitimate gripes."},{"time":608475,"text":"Mothers are much more likely"},{"time":610330,"text":"to be multi-tasking when they are at home,"},{"time":612408,"text":"and fathers, when they are at home,"},{"time":614619,"text":"are much more likely to be mono-tasking."},{"time":617578,"text":"Find a guy at home, and odds are"},{"time":620146,"text":"he is doing just one thing at a time."},{"time":623907,"text":"In fact, UCLA recently did a study"},{"time":626811,"text":"looking at the most common configuration"},{"time":629344,"text":"of family members in middle-class homes."},{"time":632390,"text":"Guess what it was?"},{"time":634123,"text":"Dad in a room by himself."},{"time":636770,"text":"According to the American Time Use Survey,"},{"time":639210,"text":"mothers still do twice as much childcare as fathers,"},{"time":642435,"text":"which is better than it was in Erma Bombeck's day,"},{"time":646034,"text":"but I still think that something she wrote"},{"time":648300,"text":"is highly relevant:"},{"time":651172,"text":"\"I have not been alone in the\nbathroom since October.\""},{"time":654890,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":659224,"text":"But here is the thing: Men are doing plenty."},{"time":664054,"text":"They spend more time with their kids"},{"time":665830,"text":"than their fathers ever spent with them."},{"time":669164,"text":"They work more paid hours, on average,"},{"time":671144,"text":"than their wives,"},{"time":672837,"text":"and they genuinely want to be good,"},{"time":674671,"text":"involved dads."},{"time":676250,"text":"Today, it is fathers, not mothers,"},{"time":679618,"text":"who report the most work-life conflict."}]},{"cues":[{"time":683729,"text":"Either way, by the way,"},{"time":685961,"text":"if you think it's hard for traditional families"},{"time":688296,"text":"to sort out these new roles,"},{"time":689920,"text":"just imagine what it's like now"},{"time":691756,"text":"for non-traditional families:"},{"time":693651,"text":"families with two dads, families with two moms,"},{"time":696246,"text":"single-parent households."},{"time":697951,"text":"They are truly improvising as they go."}]},{"cues":[{"time":702344,"text":"Now, in a more progressive country,"},{"time":706135,"text":"and forgive me here for capitulating to cliché"},{"time":708865,"text":"and invoking, yes, Sweden,"},{"time":711919,"text":"parents could rely on the state"},{"time":714840,"text":"for support."},{"time":717489,"text":"There are countries that acknowledge"},{"time":719368,"text":"the anxieties and the changing roles"},{"time":720801,"text":"of mothers and fathers."},{"time":723165,"text":"Unfortunately, the United States is not one of them,"},{"time":726429,"text":"so in case you were wondering what the U.S."},{"time":728394,"text":"has in common with Papua New Guinea and Liberia,"},{"time":733697,"text":"it's this:"},{"time":736728,"text":"We too have no paid maternity leave policy."},{"time":740455,"text":"We are one of eight known countries that does not."}]},{"cues":[{"time":747702,"text":"In this age of intense confusion,"},{"time":751273,"text":"there is just one goal upon which"},{"time":754675,"text":"all parents can agree,"},{"time":756507,"text":"and that is whether they are"},{"time":757971,"text":"tiger moms or hippie moms, helicopters or drones,"},{"time":762537,"text":"our kids' happiness is paramount."},{"time":766678,"text":"That is what it means"},{"time":768560,"text":"to raise kids in an age"},{"time":771010,"text":"when they are economically worthless"},{"time":773235,"text":"but emotionally priceless."},{"time":775480,"text":"We are all the custodians of their self-esteem."},{"time":778880,"text":"The one mantra no parent ever questions is,"},{"time":782713,"text":"\"All I want is for my children to be happy.\""},{"time":788444,"text":"And don't get me wrong:"},{"time":790157,"text":"I think happiness is a wonderful goal for a child."},{"time":795037,"text":"But it is a very elusive one."},{"time":798743,"text":"Happiness and self-confidence,"},{"time":802683,"text":"teaching children that is not like teaching them"},{"time":804664,"text":"how to plow a field."},{"time":806180,"text":"It's not like teaching them how to ride a bike."},{"time":808881,"text":"There's no curriculum for it."},{"time":811438,"text":"Happiness and self-confidence can\nbe the byproducts of other things,"},{"time":815035,"text":"but they cannot really be goals unto themselves."},{"time":818090,"text":"A child's happiness"},{"time":819756,"text":"is a very unfair burden to place on a parent."},{"time":823521,"text":"And happiness is an even more unfair burden"},{"time":826359,"text":"to place on a kid."}]},{"cues":[{"time":829199,"text":"And I have to tell you,"},{"time":831222,"text":"I think it leads to some very strange excesses."},{"time":835104,"text":"We are now so anxious"},{"time":837506,"text":"to protect our kids from the world's ugliness"},{"time":840824,"text":"that we now shield them from \"Sesame Street.\""},{"time":845576,"text":"I wish I could say I was kidding about this,"},{"time":847712,"text":"but if you go out and you buy"},{"time":850384,"text":"the first few episodes of \"Sesame Street\" on DVD,"},{"time":853323,"text":"as I did out of nostalgia,"},{"time":856404,"text":"you will find a warning at the beginning"},{"time":859517,"text":"saying that the content is not suitable"},{"time":862147,"text":"for children."},{"time":863915,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":866025,"text":"Can I just repeat that?"},{"time":867230,"text":"The content of the original \"Sesame Street\""},{"time":869861,"text":"is not suitable for children."},{"time":873203,"text":"When asked about this by The New York Times,"},{"time":876845,"text":"a producer for the show gave\na variety of explanations."},{"time":880150,"text":"One was that Cookie Monster smoked a pipe"},{"time":882909,"text":"in one skit and then swallowed it."},{"time":884670,"text":"Bad modeling. I don't know."},{"time":886105,"text":"But the thing that stuck with me"},{"time":889087,"text":"is she said that she didn't know"},{"time":891542,"text":"whether Oscar the Grouch could be invented today"},{"time":895881,"text":"because he was too depressive."},{"time":900779,"text":"I cannot tell you how much this distresses me."},{"time":903187,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":904706,"text":"You are looking at a woman"},{"time":906559,"text":"who has a periodic table of the Muppets"},{"time":909603,"text":"hanging from her cubicle wall."},{"time":913395,"text":"The offending muppet, right there."}]},{"cues":[{"time":918239,"text":"That's my son the day he was born."},{"time":923025,"text":"I was high as a kite on morphine."},{"time":925217,"text":"I had had an unexpected C-section."},{"time":929080,"text":"But even in my opiate haze,"},{"time":932596,"text":"I managed to have one very clear thought"},{"time":935529,"text":"the first time I held him."},{"time":938481,"text":"I whispered it into his ear."},{"time":940385,"text":"I said, \"I will try so hard not to hurt you.\""},{"time":949269,"text":"It was the Hippocratic Oath,"},{"time":950589,"text":"and I didn't even know I was saying it."},{"time":954467,"text":"But it occurs to me now"},{"time":956791,"text":"that the Hippocratic Oath"},{"time":958870,"text":"is a much more realistic aim than happiness."},{"time":963202,"text":"In fact, as any parent will tell you,"},{"time":966802,"text":"it's awfully hard."},{"time":969570,"text":"All of us have said or done hurtful things"},{"time":974424,"text":"that we wish to God we could take back."},{"time":980398,"text":"I think in another era"},{"time":983246,"text":"we did not expect quite so much from ourselves,"},{"time":987238,"text":"and it is important that we all remember that"},{"time":990920,"text":"the next time we are staring with our hearts racing"},{"time":994754,"text":"at those bookshelves."},{"time":1000254,"text":"I'm not really sure how to create new norms"},{"time":1003508,"text":"for this world,"},{"time":1005186,"text":"but I do think that"},{"time":1008270,"text":"in our desperate quest to create happy kids,"},{"time":1011588,"text":"we may be assuming the wrong moral burden."},{"time":1014615,"text":"It strikes me as a better goal,"},{"time":1016333,"text":"and, dare I say, a more virtuous one,"},{"time":1018549,"text":"to focus on making productive kids"},{"time":1021268,"text":"and moral kids,"},{"time":1022608,"text":"and to simply hope that happiness will come to them"},{"time":1024924,"text":"by virtue of the good that they do"},{"time":1027670,"text":"and their accomplishments"},{"time":1029898,"text":"and the love that they feel from us."},{"time":1032796,"text":"That, anyway, is one response to having no script."},{"time":1038429,"text":"Absent having new scripts,"},{"time":1041762,"text":"we just follow the oldest ones in the book --"},{"time":1045447,"text":"decency, a work ethic, love —"},{"time":1051046,"text":"and let happiness and self-esteem\ntake care of themselves."},{"time":1055370,"text":"I think if we all did that,"},{"time":1057414,"text":"the kids would still be all right,"},{"time":1060955,"text":"and so would their parents,"},{"time":1063601,"text":"possibly in both cases even better."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1067569,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1069448,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}